# App-Wide Mobile-First Guardrails

When editing components across the app:

- Keep components mobile-first.
- Do not change existing behavior for viewports below `768px`.
- Add layout changes for tablet widths using `min-width` media queries (for example, `@media (min-width: 768px)`).
- Preserve Supabase realtime/live updates exactly as-is.
- Do not refactor data fetching logic or subscription wiring.

Use additive styling/layout updates only, and avoid behavioral changes to existing mobile flows.
